'''Corrine Henley''' is the daughter of [[Roy Henley]].

==History==
Corrine came to the hospital when her father was getting new lungs. She hadn't seen him in twenty years before that day. Shortly after she arrived, his condition started rapidly deteriorating. She was worried about him and regretted having called him by his first name when she arrived. She continued to worry as his condition worsened.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She was estranged from her father after her parents divorced. She took her mother's side in the divorce, which her father didn't blame her for. She says he tried to be her father for a while, but he eventually stopped because she couldn't forgive him for leaving her mother.

She also has three year old twins and she wasn't sure if her father knew about them or not.
